data.title: CARLOS DELFINO 2013-14 TOTALLY CERTIFIED TOTALLY GOLD /25 HOUSTON ROCKETS #136
data.meta_description:
For the avid basketball card collector, here's a chance to acquire the 2013-14 Totally Certified Carlos Delfino card from the Houston Rockets. This limited edition sports trading card is a gold parallel/variety, short print insert card that's also serial numbered for added value.


Manufactured by Panini, this card set belongs to the 2013-14 season and comes in an ungraded condition. It features the player's image, name, team, and relevant information about the card. Add this rare find to your collection today!
